    <item>
      <title>随着金价接近历史最高水平，中国央行购买更多黄金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/china-s-central-bank-buys-more-gold-as-prices-trade-near-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国央行12月份连续第二个月增加黄金储备，表明在去年金价飙升导致暂停购买黄金后，中国黄金需求再度升温。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/china-s-central-bank-buys-more-gold-as-prices-trade-near-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 08:15:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称，哈萨克斯坦国家石油公司是卢克石油保加利亚炼油厂的竞标者之一</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/kazmunaygas-is-said-to-be-among-bidders-for-lukoil-s-bulgaria-refinery</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据两位了解谈判情况的人士透露，哈萨克斯坦国家石油公司 (KazMunayGas National Company JSC) 正在竞标收购俄罗斯卢克石油公司 (Lukoil PJSC) 位于保加利亚的炼油厂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/kazmunaygas-is-said-to-be-among-bidders-for-lukoil-s-bulgaria-refinery</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 06:37:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港融资成本飙升 人民币做空者受压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/offshore-yuan-borrowing-costs-surge-as-currency-support-in-focus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港人民币融资成本飙升至多年未见的水平，表明人们担心北京方面稳定人民币的努力可能会导致离岸市场流动性收紧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/offshore-yuan-borrowing-costs-surge-as-currency-support-in-focus</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 05:49:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Nickel Asia 计划向住友出售加工厂股权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/nickel-asia-aims-to-sell-processing-plant-stake-to-sumitomo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾最大的镍生产商亚洲镍业公司 (Nickel Asia Corp.) 正就将其在一家重要加工厂的少数股权出售给日本住友金属矿业公司进行谈判，因为这家公司专注于上游采矿和可再生能源业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/nickel-asia-aims-to-sell-processing-plant-stake-to-sumitomo</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 05:37:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球最大微电网公司计划募资 4 亿美元并进行 IPO</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/world-s-biggest-mini-grid-firm-aims-to-raise-400-million-plans-ipo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大的太阳能微电网运营商 Husk Power Systems 今年计划通过债务和股权融资高达 4 亿美元，创下行业纪录，其业务正在印度和非洲不断扩张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/world-s-biggest-mini-grid-firm-aims-to-raise-400-million-plans-ipo</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元因定盘价和散户投资者流入而跌至 7 月以来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/yen-weakens-to-lowest-since-july-on-fixing-retail-selling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日元兑美元汇率跌至 7 月份以来的最低水平，落后于大多数主要货币，分析师将日元下跌归因于日本散户投资者的资金流出以及东京基准汇率的定价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/yen-weakens-to-lowest-since-july-on-fixing-retail-selling</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 04:30:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税风险成为焦点，美元走弱带动黄金小幅走高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/gold-steady-as-trump-s-remarks-fan-uncertainty-across-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在当选总统唐纳德·特朗普否认有关他可能缓和全面关税计划的报道后，交易商权衡全球贸易风险，因美元疲软，金价小幅走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/gold-steady-as-trump-s-remarks-fan-uncertainty-across-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 00:24:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
